  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Continuing, Increasing and Enhancing The Free Supply of Blood Units to The Hospitals of Gaza Strip as Response to Great Return of March Events.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims at enhancing the trauma pathway by providing essential blood units  in satisfying Gaza Strip&apos;s hospitals needs freely, especially those work in emergency situation or those located in marginalized areas in southern governorates by the means increasing the blood donations campaigns ,raising the  awareness of the blood donation among  people to attract more voluntary donors, Pursuant to the statistics of ministry of health report regarding laboratories in 2017 percentage of blood donation shows that 2.3% and the rate of voluntary donors in Gaza strip that 29% of total blood donors 
It will target non-governmental institutions, universities and mosques where blood donation campaigns will be launched and implemented. the campaign includes a numerous  of activities , such as  holding orientation meetings about the process of blood donations and its benefits to the health of individual , its urgent needs in the current situation  ,and the eligibility requirements for donating ,  examining drawn blood samples of the eligible donors and then drawing blood units and examining it in the laboratories of society branches according to the standards of ministry of health and the standards of WHO in the field of blood banks.</narrative>
  </description>
